{"tid":1805574,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"踏入2020年　警旺角射催淚彈　示威者彌敦道放煙花","createTime":"2019-12-31T16:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T16:33:33.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d6dbd180d03d7ac2058e6461d644bbe3263bb4","tid":1805574,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T16:32:35.000Z","msg":"踏入2020年，警方凌晨零時許於旺角登打士街一帶施放催淚彈，一名男子右腳疑中催淚彈受傷。<br />\n<br />\n另外，於油麻地登打士街及咸美頓街一段的彌敦道，有示威者放煙花。<br />\n<br />\n在西洋菜南街，數百名市民在2019年最後10秒倒數，大叫「10、9、光、復、香、港、時、代、革、命」，同時與警方對峙。倒數後數十名防暴警向豉油街推進。<br />\n<br />\n在尖沙嘴海旁，群眾以「光復香港 時代革命」代替「Happy New Year」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200101/s00001/1577809005366/%e8%b8%8f%e5%85%a52020%e5%b9%b4-%e8%ad%a6%e6%97%ba%e8%a7%92%e5%b0%84%e5%82%ac%e6%b7%9a%e5%bd%88-%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81%e8%80%85%e5%bd%8c%e6%95%a6%e9%81%93%e6%94%be%e7%85%99%e8%8a%b1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200101%2Fs00001%2F1577809005366%2F%25e8%25b8%258f%25e5%2585%25a52020%25e5%25b9%25b4-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%2597%25ba%25e8%25a7%2592%25e5%25b0%2584%25e5%2582%25ac%25e6%25b7%259a%25e5%25bd%2588-%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%2580%2585%25e5%25bd%258c%25e6%2595%25a6%25e9%2581%2593%25e6%2594%25be%25e7%2585%2599%25e8%258a%25b1&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=8df930f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200101%2Fs00001%2F1577809005366%2F%25e8%25b8%258f%25e5%2585%25a52020%25e5%25b9%25b4-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%2597%25ba%25e8%25a7%2592%25e5%25b0%2584%25e5%2582%25ac%25e6%25b7%259a%25e5%25bd%2588-%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%2580%2585%25e5%25bd%258c%25e6%2595%25a6%25e9%2581%2593%25e6%2594%25be%25e7%2585%2599%25e8%258a%25b1&h=68bd589b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200101/s00001/15778